trans-unit.source: Provides a thread-safe collection that contains channel dispatchers.
trans-unit.target: Fornece uma coleção thread-safe que contém os distribuidores de canal.

trans-unit.source: This collection is used by <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase> to manage the channel dispatchers associated with the host.
trans-unit.target: Essa coleção é usada por <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase>para gerenciar os distribuidores de canal associadas ao host.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase>

trans-unit.source: A ChannelDispatcherCollection is created when <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.%23ctor%2A> is called and the collection can be accessed using the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Um ChannelDispatcherCollection é criado quando <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.%23ctor%2A>é chamado e a coleção pode ser acessada usando a <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: The collection contains <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> objects (and not just instances of <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher>) because it is also used by developers who want to keep the [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]programming model but replace the system-provided runtime.
trans-unit.target: A coleção contém <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>objetos (e não apenas instâncias de <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher>) porque ele também é usado por desenvolvedores que desejam manter a [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]programação de modelo, mas substituir o tempo de execução fornecida pelo sistema.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>

trans-unit.source: They derive a class from <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> and extend <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> (which inherits from <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase>) by overriding <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.InitializeRuntime%2A>, adding instances of the class derived from <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> to <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Elas derivar uma classe de <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>e estender <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>(que herda de <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase>) por meio da substituição <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.InitializeRuntime%2A>, adicionando instâncias da classe derivada da <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.InitializeRuntime%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>

trans-unit.source: This class has no public constructors and is not intended to be used outside of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não tem nenhum construtor público e não se destina a ser usada fora de <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>
